Fee-DepositTrgt: 发送到底层的农场平台, 而不是 Beefy
Fee-WithdrawTrgt: 分布于金库参与者之间。保护用户。

Boost-Explain: 当您在Beefy金库存款时，您的钱包里会收到一个前缀为 'moo'的 '收据'代币。当有一个强化池时，您可以将该代币押在此处，以获得额外的收益利益。
Remember-Msg: mooTokens 是您存款的有息代币化证明。您将需要他们来提取您的资金。失去对 mooToken 的所有权将意味着您失去对存款的所有权。
Remember-Msg-Bst: 您的 mooToken 将持续生成利息，而您将在它们之上赚取额外的代币。
Safety-ScoreExpl: 安全评分是由 Beefy 的开发人员在评估金库时计算的。没有任何分数可以完美地反映风险水平，但Beefy发现它是一个有用的决策标准。安全评分从 0 到 10（最差到最好）对金库进行排名。
Safety-HigherSafer: Beefy 安全评分越高，您的投资就越安全。
Safety-BeefySecure: 您的资金在 Beefy.Finance 上始终保持安全。团队在检查金库方面投入了大量的精力。每个金库也具有一项紧急设施，如果需要，甚至发现有可疑的活动，金库可以在短时间内停止活动，以保护用户的资金。
Gov-Info1: 通过在我们的 BIFI 收益池中质押您的 $BIFI，您可以分享平台的利润并赚取可观的收益。
Gov-Info2: 您的 APY 与 Beefy 金库产生的收入成正比，然后我们会使用这些收入直接购买 $BIFI 并奖励给您。
Gov-Info3: 您无需取消质押即可参与治理，这使它成为让您的 Beefy 声音被听到并同时获得收益的最佳方式。
Page-Not-Found: 不幸的是，Beefy Cow 似乎已经移动了您要查找的页面
QiDao-Content: 使用您的 mooTokens 作为 Mai.finance 的抵押品并铸造 MAI，只需支付 0.5% 的还款费。请注意，所有贷款都存在清算风险。
Insurace-Content: InsurAce.io 是一个去中心化的多链保险协议，可保护用户免受智能合约风险的影响。现在就以些许的费用来担保您的存款！
Moonpot-Content: Moonpot 是我们的双赢储蓄游戏。将您的加密货币存入 Moonpot，赚取利息并同时参加抽奖。
NetworkStatus-HelpText-Error: 一些数据可能显示不正确
Nexus-Content: Nexus Mutual 是一个基于区块链的传统保险的替代方案。成为 Mutual 会员，为您的 Beefy 仓位购买全面保险。
Solace-Content: Insure your portfolio against smart contract risks with a personalized policy that dynamically updates coverage as your portfolio changes. No need to file a claim when you lose funds. Payouts arrive within one week.
beFTM-description: beFTM 意味着 Beefy Escrowed Fantom。该代币与FTM挂钩，可以质押于Beefy平台，并在主要去中心化交易所进行耕种。BeFTM 让质押者能够获得最大化的验证者奖励，而个人投资者在不锁定 FTM 一年的情况下通常无法获得这些奖励。
Mint-Reminder: {{token1}} is minted at a 1:1 ratio with {{token2}}. If {{token1}}'s price is under peg when a user attempts to mint, {{token1}} will instead be purchased at the better market rate.
Mint-Content: Lock your {{token2}} to get {{token1}}. Each {{token1}} is backed by 1 {{token2}}.
Mint-Content-Burnable: Mint {{token1}} by depositing {{token2}}. {{token1}} can be staked into a Beefy Vault. {{token1}} can be exchanged back to {{token2}} when there is a supply in our reserves.
Mint-Content-Burnable-Earnings: Mint {{token1}} by depositing {{token2}}. {{token1}} can be staked into a Beefy Vault or Earnings Pool. {{token1}} can be exchanged back to {{token2}} when there is a supply in our reserves.
Burn-Content: Burn {{token1}} for {{token2}} when there is {{token2}} in reserves. Our reserves increase when users deposit {{token2}} for {{token1}}.
beJOE-description: beJOE is Beefy Staked JOE. The token is pegged to JOE and can be staked on the Beefy platform to earn JOE or more beJOE. beJOE gives stakers access to 5% of all Beefy Trader Joe Boosted farm rewards. You can burn beJOE for JOE if there is available JOE reserves.
beQI-description: beQI is Beefy Staked QI. The token is pegged to QI and can be staked on the Beefy platform to earn QI or more beQI. beQI gives stakers access to max lock rewards of staking QI for eQI. You can burn beQI for QI if there is available QI reserves.
MaxNativeAlert: You can't deposit 100% of your {{token}} into vault, make sure you leave enough gas for future transactions
InfoCard-binSPIRIT-Title: Vote on SPIRIT Emissions with binSPIRIT
InfoCard-binSPIRIT-Work-Text: SpiritSwap’s inSPIRIT governance token uses a vote locking model. binSPIRIT is a wrapped version of 4-year-locked inSPIRIT. inSPIRIT & binSPIRIT holders receive voting power, participation rewards, and boosted farming rewards. binSPIRIT holders can vote weekly on the gauges to receive SPIRIT emission allocation.
InfoCard-binSPIRIT-Bribes-Title: Use Beefy’s Voting Power to Earn Bribes
InfoCard-binSPIRIT-Bribes-Text: 50% of Beefy’s voting rights from locking SPIRIT are given to binSPIRIT holders. Beefy distributes these rights to binSPIRIT users to vote weekly via Snapshot. There is an open bribe environment for projects to bribe binSPIRIT holders for their voting power. Voters will receive bribes via an airdrop generated from the voting history.
